name: 230501_2409_2-2_FR_DoveComing.wav
description:
Collared dove coming to her nest. 
I made this recording during a spring morning, on a 4th floor balcony located in Nice city (south-east of France). While a dove was putting the finishing touch to her nest. The microphones were clipped on the side wall of the balcony, about 20cm under the nest. 
Here, the dove is coming. First, she goes to the metallic fences of the balcony, then comes to her nest, makes some small adjustments, before keeping almost silent. In the background, seagulls, other doves, some birds chirping, a moped passing by in the distance, a cat meowing and an airplane flying over. 
Recorded in May 2023 with an Olympus LS-P4 and Micbooster Clippy Stereo EM272 microphones (Primo em272). 
Fade in/out and high pass filter at 30Hz -6dB/oct applied in Audacity. 
(If you want to use this sound as a mono audio file, you may have to delete one channel to avoid phase issues).
